data.name: 北京浮生记
data.describe: 您扮演一位从外地到北京谋生的青年。一开始，您只有 2000 元钱，并且还欠村长（一个流氓头子）5000 元债务。这些债务每天的利息高达 10%。  如果不及时还清，村长会叫在北京的老乡们来扁您，您可能牺牲在北京街头。您决定在北京各地铁口黑市倒卖各种物品来发财致富，不仅还掉债务，而且要荣登北京富人排行榜。  您只能在北京呆 40 天，每次奔走一个黑市算一天。一开始，您租的房子只能放 100 个东西。您会在北京遭遇到各种事件，您需要与流氓，小偷，凶手，贪官，骗子等斗智斗勇，还需要在北京恶劣的自然环境下设法生存下来。

ai_content.synopsis: Beijing Flop Life on ChatGPT is a simulation game where you play as a young person trying to make a living in Beijing. Starting with only 2000 yuan and a debt of 5000 yuan to a local gang leader, you must navigate the city, selling various items at the black market near subway stations to earn money and pay off your debt. But beware of the daily 10% interest on your debt, which could lead to severe consequences if not paid in time. Your ultimate goal is to not only clear your debt but also climb the ranks of Beijing's wealthy elite. With a limited time of 40 days and a restricted inventory space of 100 items in your rented house, you will encounter various challenges including encounters with gangsters, thieves, murderers, corrupt officials, and con artists while also dealing with the harsh natural environment of Beijing.
